OL,3,CUK asylum applications hit record
OL,4,Chigh, but government grants fewer work
OL,5,Cvisas
OL,7,FThe number of people applying for
OL,8,Fasylum in the UK hit a record high in
OL,9,F2024, according to new figures
OL,10,Freleased by the Home Office on
OL,11,FThursday.
OL,13,FApplications last year were up by 18%
OL,14,Ffrom 2023 and the total number was
OL,15,Fhigher than it has been for more than
OL,16,F20 years.
OL,18,FThe total for 2024 was 108,138 people
OL,19,Fapplying for asylum, higher than the
OL,20,Fprevious record of 103,081 in 2002.
