OL,7,FAsked why the numbers were so high,
OL,8,FHome Office Minister Angela Eagle
OL,9,Fsaid: "I think that we've got to
OL,10,Fremember that in the last six years
OL,11,Fmigration soared.
OL,13,F"We were left a broken asylum system
OL,14,Fby the previous government, literally
OL,15,Fasylum decision making collapsed by
OL,16,F70% in the last few months before the
OL,17,Felection and we inherited a huge
OL,18,Fbacklog of asylum claims.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
