OL,7,F"It will take time to make certain
OL,8,Fthat we can get a grip and start
OL,9,Fmaking the system work."
OL,11,FMigrants who arrived in the UK after
OL,12,Fcrossing the English Channel in small
OL,13,Fboats accounted for 32% of those
OL,14,Fclaiming asylum. Pakistani was the
OL,15,Fmost common nationality among
OL,16,Fapplicants (9.7%), followed by people
OL,17,Fborn in Afghanistan.
