OL,7,FAlongside the new claims made last
OL,8,Fyear, there were still 124,802 people
OL,9,Fwaiting for an initial decision on
OL,10,Ftheir asylum application at the end of
OL,11,FDecember 2024.
OL,13,FThe number of quarterly enforced
OL,14,Freturns of people who do not have a
OL,15,Fright to stay in the UK also rose last
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FSome 2,364 enforced returns took place
OL,19,Fin October to December 2024.
