OL,12,FThe new data also outlined that fewer
OL,13,Fwork visas were granted by the
OL,14,Fgovernment last year.
OL,16,FSome 210,000 visas were approved in
OL,17,F2024, fewer than the previous year but
OL,18,Fsignificantly higher than in 2019.
