OL,3,CUK asylum applications hit record
OL,4,Chigh, but government grants fewer work
OL,5,Cvisas
OL,7,FIn the Health and Care sector, 27,000
OL,8,Fvisas were successful, 81% fewer than
OL,9,Fthe peak in 2023.
OL,11,FThe largest decrease was in the food
OL,12,Fand hospitality sector, where the
OL,13,Fnumber of visas granted fell by 64%.
OL,15,FThere was also a fall in number of
OL,16,Fstudents successfully applying for
OL,17,Fvisas to study in the UK.
