OL,7,FHowever, the number of 'Temporary
OL,8,FWorker' visas granted almost doubled,
OL,9,Fand there was a 7% increase in the
OL,10,Fnumber of people who already have
OL,11,Ffamily in the UK being given visas.
OL,13,FResponding to the figures on Thursday,
OL,14,FMarley Morris, from the Institute for
OL,15,FPublic Policy Research think tank,
OL,16,Fsaid: "If the Home Office wants to end
OL,17,Fthe use of hotels, it will need to
OL,18,Fdouble down on efforts to improve the
OL,19,Fspeed and quality of decision-making.
