OL,7,F"Applications should be triaged early
OL,8,Fand decisions for high-grant
OL,9,Fnationalities should be streamlined.
OL,11,F"Crucially, the Government must take
OL,12,Fcare that its efforts to accelerate
OL,13,Fdecision-making do not result in these
OL,14,Fcases simply shifting over into
OL,15,Fappeals."
OL,17,FThe Border Security, Asylum and
OL,18,FImmigration Bill was being discussed
OL,19,Fby MP's in Parliament on Thursday.
